Date: Mon, 4 May 2026 08:46:10 -0400
Subject: [PATCH 5/6] UI: Eversense customizations (TIR rename, transmitter
 battery, plugin icon)

- Rename 'Dexcom TIR' header to 'Eversense TIR' in Statistics across 10 locales
- Add Eversense plugin icon (IcPluginEversense)
- Add transmitter battery percentage to Overview status lights
